Name: Average duration of 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' before transitioning to 'Accepted + In Progress'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Total duration of all 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' activities within a case
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Queued + Awaiting Assignment and the end of the case

Name: Minimum duration of 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' across all cases
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Queued + Awaiting Assignment and the end of the case

Name: Average duration from 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' to 'Completed + In Call' compared to 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Total duration from 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' to 'Accepted + In Progress' across all variants where this transition occurs
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Minimum duration from 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' to 'Accepted + In Progress' in cases leading to 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Total duration of 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' in cases that eventually lead to 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Duration of 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' in the fastest case to reach 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Queued + Awaiting Assignment and the end of the case

Name: Duration of 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' in the slowest case to reach 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000001A843391A90> - AppliesTo.PROCESS filtered by the function ma > 0 where ma is the number of times `ACTIVITY` == 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Total duration of 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' activities before reaching any 'Accepted + Wait' state
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Wait'

Name: Minimum duration of 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' before any 'Completed + Resolved' activity
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average duration from 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' to the next activity in the most frequent process variant
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and the end of case where activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment does not occur

Name: Duration of 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' in cases that do not transition directly to 'Accepted + In Progress'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and the end of case where activity 'Accepted + In Progress does not occur

Name: Average duration of 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' in cases with high impact versus cases with low impact
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and the end of case grouped by the last value of impact filtered by the function ma == 'high' where ma is the last value of impact
